messages.message: Feedback on build mode — getting great answers when I’m building the app, but wrong / incomplete answers on the exact same document when I actually run the application
@Lee wasn't this the issue you had last week?
Testing now

Yep, the bug I reported before the prod deployment in UAT has made it to prod
Thanks @Lee. @Varun Jain do we know how this could happen (i.e. a material bug flagged during UAT was still shipped to Prod)?
